TESTS
==================================================

## Pre-requirements
phpunit

## Launching tests

### Command-line
cd ROOT_DIR (ie: /home/user/RevPDFLib)
phpunit

### Netbeans
Under Project Properties > Sources,
set Test Folder: /path/to/RevPDFLib/tests
Under Project Properties > PHPUnit,
set "User XML Configuration": /path/to/RevPDFLib/phpunit.xml.dist